<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd" []>
<concept xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="specifying-document-editing-preferences" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:concept.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Specifying Document Editing Preferences</title>
  <conbody id="body">
    <p>Document editing preferences include the following:<ol>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-default-spelling-dictionary.xml">Default spelling dictionary</xref>.</p>
          <p>You can check your document for spelling mistakes. Serna comes with English spell-checking dictionaries only (US, GB, and Canadian), but you are free to add more dictionaries and specify the default one.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="specifying-undo-redo-stack-depth.xml">Undo/Redo stack depth</xref>.</p>
          <p conref="specifying-undo-redo-stack-depth.xml#specifying-undo-redo-depth/undo-redo-intro"/>
        </li>
      </ol></p>
  </conbody>
</concept>
